iebaker.neon.world

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • iebaker.neon.world.Entity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bush, Robot

    public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    Entity is a class representing an entity which is capable of occupying a grid square in CellWorld. An entity has a position, a parent world, and a plan consisting of a series of vertices which it may use to move around the world.
